---
title: "US24 — Follow other users"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UserProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>FollowUser / UnfollowUser
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SocialGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: tap "Add Friend"
  B->>C: follow(userId)
  C->>G: insert follows
  G-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: following
  B-->>A: button now "Unfriend" - their posts join the feed
